description:
Gillette Venus Sensitive Disposable Razors, provide a close shave and silky smooth skin in just one stroke.

This disposable women’s shaving razor features a 3-bladed, pivoting head and a comfortable handle for an extra-close shave and easy glide.

- Extra lubricants for glide.

- Gentle smoothness in 1 stroke.

- 3 Blades+ Moisture strips with more lubricants vs Venus Original.

- Pivoting rounded head to fit easily into hard to shave areas.

- Lubrastrip, with a touch of aloe, for glide.

Up to 100% Smoothness for Sensitive Skin*

3 blades surrounded by soft, protective cushions

Pivoting, rounded head to fit easily into hard-to-shave areas

Specially designed handle for great control

No razor blade change required; just use and toss
name: Gillette Venus Sensitive Disposable Razors 3 Pack
